        <h2>Career Journey</h2>
        <p>
          My career journey has been a progressive path from internships to senior engineering roles, with a focus on software development, platform building, and leading technical initiatives.
        </p>
      </section>
    </AnimatedSection>

    <AnimatedSection delay={0.3} client:load>
      <section>
        <h2>Work Experience</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3>Senior Software Engineer - Platform at Rippling</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Aug 2024 - Present (6 months)</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Building platform for future work applications</li>
            <li>Leading Data globalization initiatives</li>
            <li>Building Dependency Tracking</li>
