        </div>

        <div>
          <h3>Staff Software Engineer (Uber TL), Banking at Slice</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Nov 2023 - Aug 2024 (10 months)</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Led banking initiatives for various systems</li>
            <li>Designed workflows and introduced Temporal</li>
            <li>Built AI-driven code reviewer and PR summary tool</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3>Tech Lead - A2, CI/CD Infra, Developer Productivity at Slice</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Nov 2022 - Nov 2023 (1 year 1 month)</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Revamped CI/CD pipelines for 250+ engineers</li>
            <li>Migrated workload from ECS to K8s</li>
            <li>Led personal loan onboarding product development</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3>SDE II, Acquisition & Activation at Slice</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Jun 2022 - Nov 2022 (6 months)</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Worked with AWS tools</li>
            <li>Fixed older code and processes</li>
            <li>Built a new product from ground up</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
