            <li>Implemented various backend optimizations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3>SDE II at Vedantu</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Apr 2021 - Dec 2021 (9 months)</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Designed Logging platform with Kafka</li>
            <li>Migrated legacy services, reducing costs</li>
            <li>Developed collaborative assignment system</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3>SDE I - Live Class Platform at Vedantu</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Jul 2020 - Apr 2021 (10 months)</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Moved legacy service to Kubernetes</li>
            <li>Scaled video conversion platform</li>
