        </div>

        <div>
          <h3>Software Engineering Intern at Vedantu</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Jan 2020 - Apr 2020 (4 months)</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Automated UAT environment creation</li>
            <li>Worked on in-house video streaming capabilities</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3>Google Summer of Code (Wikimedia) - Summer Intern</h3>
